# Purpose: Stdlib-only HTML-to-Markdown converter targeting Canvas LMS HTML
#          patterns. Used by page download and discussion export scripts.
# Usage: Imported by CLI scripts.
# Input: HTML string (Canvas page body, discussion entry message, etc.)
# Output: Markdown string.
